name: #1 ElfenWander
description: ElfenWander refers to the dreamy places I've visited in Tushetii, wandering from mountain to mountain. It's also wandering through some preenFM2 synth settings. #1 in the modularmountain series, artwork for bandcamp album found here https://kaotec.bandcamp.com/  The music was inspired on the picture, composed while I was there. The visuals were inspired on the music, overdubbed on the picture. They are dynamic clojure(quil) patches, live coded in conjunction with live patched modular music.
